popup_html_about_text.message:
The Hive Keychain team is led by @stoodkev, a developer and Hive witness, and consists of a total of 3 full-time developers at the moment. We also benefit from the help of @nateaguila, Splinterlands's Creative Director, and many other community members.

While the project is currently funded through the Decentralized Hive Fund (DHF), the original idea and funds were provided by @aggroed and @yabapmatt (witnesses) through their joint business Splinterlands, a blockchain-based collectible trading card game built on top of the Hive blockchain. Be sure to check it out at https://splinterlands.io!

For more information on our products (browser extensions and mobile Apps), visit our landing page.
